name: The New Illusion
description:
Are we sure that we're born in a reality dimension? Living on a real society? Eating a real food and poop on a real toilet? Sometimes, dreams happens. Dying is only dream. Life is like a fake reality. Are we confused? We dont think so. We just stay on the recent dimension that we found after sleep. Woke up early morning to make sure that we're still alive. So welcome to the new illusion. Every breath that we take before another illusion. Another flower dimension. Another love confusion. So welcome.
